---
title: Blue Corn Tortilla Skillet with Eggs, Black Beans, Lime Crema, Pickled Onion & Pepper Jack
description: Blue corn tortillas are not only a snacking favorite, but trust our chefs here: they add the perfect crunch to any Southwest-inspired meal. This skillet dinner has a delicious mix of hearty beans, fried eggs, pickled onion, and Tex-Mex spiced blue corn tortilla chips. It’s all topped with gooey melted pepper jack and a drizzle of tangy lime crema all over. Are you ready to dig in?
